snippet.title: Sega Saturn - Private Idol Disc Vol 07 - Asou Kaori (1997)

DESCRIPTION
Private Idol Disc Vol. 7: Asou Kaori is a Miscellaneous game, developed and published by Sada Soft, which was released in Japan in 1997.
